{"tid":2432822,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［新任務］要學識唔能夠再俾新聞影響到自己情緒！","createTime":"2021-03-04T14:37:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T14:51:14.000Z","uid":219007,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a133f3efea176dc70aaa7bc892f9fda3cd64851b","tid":2432822,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T14:37:52.000Z","msg":"就算你做返2019年既事，都唔會改變到啲乜嘢。出到黎又鳩企等人衝，每日拉100人，星期一香港人記億format到星期五？結果又要死多幾多人？除非有信心規模大過2019，否則咪撚搞。<br />\n<br />\n無錯你屋企俾人入侵左，但係佢有槍有炮，你乜撚都無唔夠揪，係理性下唯有離開。唔夠揪又唔憤氣於是衝左出下，下埸就係死得好轟烈，呢啲叫做衝動，而衝動嘅往往就係後生仔，因為後生仔性格燥動。<br />\n<br />\n留得係到唯有靠意志生存，信念係冇錯唔會變，但久而久之好多人都會因為經濟而決定向社會現實妥協，到最後連你自己都可能會係咁。<br />\n<br />\n一係走，否則無乜野做到。而人係要過活，大家要學識唔能夠再比新聞影響到自己情緒，唔開心打舖機，否則好難生存會自殺。"},{"pid":"2b8c57a8f3171306ac36f140eb6a72b5d9376114","tid":2432822,"uid":114193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T14:38:35.000Z","msg":"做順民輕鬆面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為連下sir 忠實信徒<br />\n堅決支持連下sir 信念：<br />\n反黑暴，保政權，黃屍港毒一齊攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等我copy連下sir 每日嘅大作你哋睇<br />\n震懾下你班連登黑暴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中大DQ學生會一事足以證明只能放棄香港，留底只能夠選擇表忠。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2423210\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2423210</a><br />\n<br />\n「安心出行」根本就冇得避，留底既香港人只會能夠接受～<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2401117\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2401117</a><br />\n<br />\n依家講到明連選舉都唔俾你玩，請問啲留港抗爭撚點睇？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2417881\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2417881</a><br />\n<br />\n［改變心態］香港變成點唔重要，最緊要自己活得開心就足夠！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2368342\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2368342</a><br />\n<br />\n聖誕節，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2329311/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2329311/page/1</a><br />\n肥佬黎俾人告國安法，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2323506/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2323506/page/1</a><br />\n中大畢業遊行，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2315353/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2315353/page/1</a><br />\n拜登贏咗，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2276817/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2276817/page/1</a><br />\n就黎國安法實行，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2184746/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2184746/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2073990/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2073990/page/1</a><br />\n612一周年，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2046361/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2046361/page/1</a><br />\n有武肺，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1850160/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1850160/page/1</a><br />\nPoly 打完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1768364/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1768364/page/1</a><br />\n要選區議會，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1681018/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1681018/page/1</a><br />\n機場壓力測試完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1548844/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1548844/page/1</a><br />\n8月大罷工完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1417635/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1417635/page/1</a><br />\n728元朗遊行完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1383029/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1383029/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"ad5d40a202e7c0ea1e5d67f7af0bc385cc32363a","tid":2432822,"uid":114193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T14:41:34.000Z","msg":"加埋今日呢篇<br />\n<br />\n今次大審判係成功將非建制派連根拔起，抗爭力量或從此永無翻身之日。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2432012\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2432012</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"de4bcaa854af3f65fbaf3847cfe495e527c618e4","tid":2432822,"uid":114193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T14:42:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"429d0e4bf0e6232cb3d23092a1dc32e8c36773f6","tid":2432822,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T14:44:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8762c518ea9a24c4418e89a23ae39116adc175b8","tid":2432822,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T14:46:30.000Z","msg":"不停喺度後退底線<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ae6c3da56b1bc52bf289e6950d018e65f5f6366","tid":2432822,"uid":381291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T14:49:37.000Z","msg":"blocked"},{"pid":"cca1c639446251e7819378667c61db14bb64bb35","tid":2432822,"uid":114193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T14:51:14.000Z","msg":"連下sir叫人唔理新聞<br />\n自己就狂post 新聞<br />\n今日已經五六個通知（請自行起底）<br />\n作為你忠實fans 好混亂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}